reviewText: watched again and again, great stuff.

The production of these videos of Inspector Maigret is excellent.  The acting is excellent, the stories are very good, and I would love to see more of the Maigret stories by the same crew.  Very enjoyable.

I ordered this a a gift for my parents and they love it. They say that there's really nothing of quality and entertainment on TV to their liking anymore, so they put the Maigret mysteries in as they please, and watch with delight. They like it so much, they really want me to watch them (tapes) too sometime. I'm sure next time I'm home, that's exactly what I'll do.
